{"tid":1417003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍有89位義士被捕！！！","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:55:15.000Z","uid":210285,"like":123,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"21d1e69dc33e7f90e9e4bd40938ec8a635392579","tid":1417003,"uid":210285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:52:28.000Z","msg":"<strong>今日戰線好多<br />\n但天水圍手足都需要大家關注</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n截至下晝4點已經拉咗76個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jjvoHcS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjjvoHcS.png&h=79141df6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ntear gas放題 出橡膠子彈 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/76AoHc3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F76AoHc3.png&h=ca8f578a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWceOS3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWceOS3.png&h=98c87c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那01仲話有裝甲車back up<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今日大西北戰況好慘烈<br />\n幫手救下未知身分嘅被捕義士</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[2324] 律師依然處理被捕人士資料 抱歉未能向各位家長更新到任何相關資訊 現時89位義士只有56位有名字/身份證 其他還需要大家提供協助🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\nSource: (tg group)天水圍救人小隊channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/市民再到天水圍警署外示威-防暴警拘數十示威者/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%86%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%96%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%81%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%2F&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=1a65beaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.k